eventText: Shrinath, Piyush wrote to Dominik for any feedback on the Amyloidosis app.

Sharyu raises the issue of copyright of page 11 (4.0.0.0 Pathogenesis) document. Sylvia says that, you do not need permission to link to a website that is publicly accessible. However, it is better if the link directs the user outside of the app and the website opens in a new window.
Sharyu tells Dominik that we will be using the DOI link provided by Sylvia.
Amyloidosis app is uploaded for internal BBI testing.
Sharyu informs Dominik about the new testflight version.
Sambhaji requests Shrinath to send Amyloidosis app to Dominik. Bugs will be solved later before uploading.
Amyloidosis app is sent to Dominik, Frank  for checking. Shrinath infromed via email.
Sharyu has contacted Dominik for any new updates on the Amyloidosis app.
Dominik sends email to Sharyu that still no feedback from client, but client will send some feedback soon.
